reviews.review_text: 1992-06-23 my first show lucky i got 4 of jerry's last years i say this now after so many years but thank u for sharing  bummer they wont let us share sbd's anymore as i am turning all my tapes into digital media lucky i had good taper fiends. anyhow on the show it was not the beast but they pulled out almost all my favs will never forget this show
